body_html:
@vrv it it not a problem in tensorflow BUILD files. It is in bazel (android rules). I have added you to cc on the fix @lberki has created.

It is happening with bazel 0.1.2 release which you can download from github (and bazel.io). IT was also happening on release 0.1.3 branch a couple of days ago. But we have a fix for it now. Just release it and we are good.
